data.description: Incredible investment opportunity in the North Side!! Interior of the house has already been demo'd, just waiting for someone to finish the renovation process. First floor has open floor plan, spacious bedrooms on second floor with big closets, and beautiful third floor loft space. Tons of natural light throughout the whole house. Unfinished basement perfect for extra storage and  Initial clean out, electrical service installation, full interior demo, rear addition demo, garage demo, and yard clean up already completed - now ready for your finishing touches! Unbeatable location - can walk to shops, cafes, restaurants, hospitals, museums, parks, and more!
